Share Repurchase Program 

&#160; 

On April 22, 2022, the Board of Directors approved a share repurchase program (the &#8220;Program&#8221;) authorizing the Company to repurchase up to $ 300,000 of the common shares of Garmin Ltd. The timing and volume of share repurchases are subject to market conditions, business conditions and applicable laws, and are at management&#8217;s discretion. Share repurchases may be made from time to time in the open market or in privately negotiated transactions, including under plans complying with the provisions of Rule 10b5-1 and Rule 10b-18 of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended. The Program does not require the purchase of any minimum number of shares and may be suspended or discontinued at any time. The share repurchase authorization expires on December 29, 2023 . 

&#160; 

